%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor USER as EPMS User
    participant UI as EPMS UI / Dashboard
    participant KPI as KPI / Reporting Service
    participant SCH as EPMS Scheduler
    participant INT as Integration Adapter
    participant JEN as Jenkins
    participant DB as EPMS Metrics DB
    participant CACHE as Redis Cache
    participant MB as Message Broker

    Note over SCH,INT: Scheduled pull every 30  / 60 minutes or on demand

    SCH->>INT: Trigger Jenkins metrics sync
    INT->>JEN: GET /api/json
    JEN-->>INT: Job list

    loop For each configured Jenkins job
        INT->>JEN: GET job details builds[number,result,duration,timestamp,url]
        JEN-->>INT: Build summary

        alt New or updated build found
            INT->>JEN: GET Job build details 
            JEN-->>INT: Build details

            opt Stage-level details needed
                INT->>JEN: GET stage details for build
                JEN-->>INT: Stage status and durations
            end

            opt Test metrics needed
                INT->>JEN: GET test metrics 
                JEN-->>INT: Passed / failed / skipped test summary
            end

            opt Failure analysis needed
                INT->>JEN: GET Failure details for failed build
                JEN-->>INT: Console log
            end

            INT->>INT: Transform Jenkins payload to EPMS schema
            INT->>DB: Upsert pipeline run / stage / test / log summary
            INT->>CACHE: Refresh latest KPI cache
            INT->>MB: Publish build status event
        end
    end

    USER->>UI: Open DevOps / Delivery dashboard
    UI->>KPI: Request Jenkins KPIs
    KPI->>CACHE: Get cached KPI summary

    alt Cache hit
        CACHE-->>KPI: KPI summary
    else Cache miss
        KPI->>DB: Query aggregated build / stage / test metrics
        DB-->>KPI: KPI dataset
        KPI->>CACHE: Update cache
    end

    KPI-->>UI: Build health / duration / failure / deployment metrics
    UI-->>USER: Display dashboard